ivardefs.name: bodySite
ivardefs.desc: Physical service site on the patient (limb, tooth, etc.).

ivardefs.name: detailSequence_
ivardefs.desc: The sequence number of the details within the claim item which this line is intended to replace.

ivardefs.name: detail_
ivardefs.desc: The second-tier service adjudications for payor added services.

ivardefs.name: factor
ivardefs.desc: A real number that represents a multiplier used in determining the overall value of services delivered and/or goods received. The concept of a Factor allows for a discount or surcharge multiplier to be applied to a monetary amount.

ivardefs.name: itemSequence_
ivardefs.desc: Claim items which this service line is intended to replace.

ivardefs.name: modifier_
ivardefs.desc: Item typification or modifiers codes to convey additional context for the product or service.

ivardefs.name: net
ivardefs.desc: The quantity times the unit price for an additional service or product or charge.

ivardefs.name: noteNumber_
ivardefs.desc: The numbers associated with notes below which apply to the adjudication of this item.

ivardefs.name: productOrService
ivardefs.desc: When the value is a group code then this item collects a set of related claim details, otherwise this contains the product, service, drug or other billing code for the item.

ivardefs.name: programCode_
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the program under which this may be recovered.

ivardefs.name: provider_
ivardefs.desc: The providers who are authorized for the services rendered to the patient.

ivardefs.name: quantity
ivardefs.desc: The number of repetitions of a service or product.

ivardefs.name: subdetailSequence_
ivardefs.desc: The sequence number of the sub-details within the details within the claim item which this line is intended to replace.

ivardefs.name: subSite_
ivardefs.desc: A region or surface of the bodySite, e.g. limb region or tooth surface(s).

ivardefs.name: unitPrice
ivardefs.desc: If the item is not a group then this is the fee for the product or service, otherwise this is the total of the fees for the details of the group.

properties.desc: The first-tier service adjudications for payor added product or service lines.
